&lt;p>The &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/t_XHw7LVy8s">video recording of this talk&lt;/a> is on YouTube,
and this is the first video posted on the
&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@HEIRCompiler">new HEIR YouTube channel&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
